flowchart TD
    A((Start)) --> B[Admin requests rollback operation]
    
    B --> C{Verify Admin Privileges}
    C -- Invalid/Denied --> D[Display Access Denied Message]
    D --> End_Denied((End))
    
    C -- Valid --> E[Admin accesses Audit Logs]
    E --> F[Extract and display activity history]
    F --> G[Admin selects target state T-1]
    G --> H[Initiate Rollback to time T-1]
    
    H --> I[System commands database restoration]
    I --> J[DBMS cancels recent critical operations]
    
    J --> K[Execute Rollback process]
    K --> L{Restoration Successful?}
    
    L -- No --> M[Abort Rollback & Alert Admin]
    M --> N((End))
    
    L -- Yes --> O[Confirm complete data restoration]
    O --> P[Save 'Rollback Executed' in Audit Log]
    P --> Q[Display success message on screen]
    Q --> R((End))